Articles.Content:
Hey everyone I recently made an F-22 raptor, it flies excellent. The fastest it has been was 230 m/s without the missiles and with them it goes around 205 m/s. The missiles do add a bit of weight but they are fun to fire and mess around with. The downloads are at the bottom one with the missiles and one without them. Enjoy ![:D](//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif)
